archimate:Facility.name: Plymouth
archimate:Facility.documentation: 34 boxes Initial indications were that they contained a mixture of Audits, Transfer and closure of branch records, and one bag full of various mixed up audit/branch visit paperwork for dates between 2016/2018. In one bag there were 11 files / paperwork around suspensions, court papers and interviews with branches regarding losses in the period 2003 to 2014. There is also a report in an audit of other branches where a robbery has taken place.
